    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<p>We are pleased to announce that Liferay DXP Quarterly Release 2026.Q1 LTS is now available for download.<br>\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>The key highlights for this Quarterly Release are:</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>New Liferay Headless CMS - <span class=\"ml-rte-link-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/e/release-notes/release-highlights/20004/27626917?r=27626917#:~:text=Management%20System%20(CMS)-,New%20Liferay%20Headless%20CMS,-Easier%20Content%20Management\">Learn More</a></span></li>\n\t<li>Hubspot Lead Capture - <a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/e/release-notes/release-highlights/20004/27626917?r=27626917#:~:text=Marketplace-,HubSpot%20Lead%20Capture,-Eliminate%20Data%20Silos\">Learn More</a></li>\n\t<li>Promote Content Among Environments - <a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/e/release-notes/release-highlights/20004/27626917?r=27626917#:~:text=Platform-,Promote%20Content%20Among%20Environments,-Easily%20Promote%20Content\">Learn More</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>To learn more about all the new features available in 2026.Q1 LTS Quarterly Release, please review the <a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/e/release-notes/release-highlights/20004/27626917?r=27626917\">Release Notes</a>.</p>\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://customer.liferay.com/en/downloads?p_p_id=com_liferay_osb_customer_downloads_display_web_DownloadsDisplayPortlet&amp;_com_liferay_osb_customer_downloads_display_web_DownloadsDisplayPortlet_productAssetCategoryId=122235468&amp;_com_liferay_osb_customer_downloads_display_web_DownloadsDisplayPortlet_fileTypeAssetCategoryId=122235708\">View Available Downloads</a></h3>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<hr>\n<p><a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/w/anatomy-of-a-quarterly-release\"><strong><u>Anatomy of a Quarterly Release</u></strong></a><br>\nLearn more about the file and folder structures for Quarterly Releases.</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/w/liferay-dxp-quarterly-release-process\"><strong><u>Frequently Asked Questions</u></strong></a><br>\nSee more important information about our DXP Platform versioning and release cadence.</p>\n\n<p><u><strong><a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/w/liferay-dxp-2026.q1-lts-compatibility-matrix\">DXP 2026.Q1 LTS Compatibility Matrix</a></strong></u><br>\nCheck compatibility here to ensure a smooth and&nbsp;supported upgrade</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://learn.liferay.com/w/dxp/self-hosted-installation-and-upgrades\"><strong><u>Installation Instructions</u></strong></a><br>\nLearn how to install DXP Quarterly Releases.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"
      },
